@startuml network-transition-sequence
!include _standard-style.puml

title Network Transition — VPN Disconnect & Recovery

actor "User" as U
participant "MacBook\n(macOS)" as MAC #F5F5F5
participant "Cisco\nAnyConnect" as VPN #E8F4FD
participant "Proxydetox\n(port 3128)" as PD #FFF2E6
participant "Health\nCoordinator" as HC #E8F5E8
participant "OpenCode\nSession" as OC #E6F3FF
participant "Corporate\nFirewall" as FW #FFEBEE
participant "api.github.com" as GH #F5F5F5

== Steady State: Connected via VPN ==

OC -> PD: CONNECT api.github.com:443
PD -> FW: HTTPS (via VPN tunnel)
FW --> PD: 200 OK (github allowed)
PD --> OC: response
note right of OC: Session works

== User Disconnects VPN ==

U -> VPN: Disconnect
VPN -> MAC: Remove utun interface\nRemove corporate DNS
MAC --> VPN: done

note over PD #FFEBEE
  PAC URL (muc.proxy-pac.bmwgroup.net)
  no longer resolvable.
  Proxydetox confused — port open
  but can't proxy requests.
end note

OC -> PD: CONNECT api.github.com:443
PD --> OC: **error** (proxy broken)
note right of OC #FFEBEE: Request fails!

== Health Coordinator Detects & Heals (within 5s) ==

HC -> HC: dig muc.proxy-pac.bmwgroup.net\n→ NXDOMAIN\nlocation = **open**
HC -> PD: functional probe → **fail**
HC -> HC: auto-heal: kickstart proxydetox

note over PD #E8F5E8
  Proxydetox restarts.
  PAC unreachable → falls back
  to **DIRECT** mode.
end note

HC -> PD: functional probe → **pass**
HC -> HC: proxy_functional = true\nlocation = open

== OpenCode Recovers (next request) ==

OC -> PD: CONNECT api.github.com:443
PD -> GH: HTTPS (**direct**, no proxy needed)
GH --> PD: 200 OK
PD --> OC: response
note right of OC #E8F5E8: Session works again!\nNo manual px-px needed.

@enduml
